The United States supports Ukraine's efforts to form an inclusive government and prepare for elections. They urge all parties involved to support reconciliation and the country's return to stability. The US will work with the international community to provide economic assistance based on Ukraine's progress in forming a unity government. They call on Ukraine's leaders to protect the rights of all citizens, honor international obligations, and avoid divisive policies. Outside actors are urged to respect Ukraine's sovereignty, support transitional governing structures, and promote unity. All governments are reminded of their commitments to transparency in military activities for peace and security in the region.